Create a Component Pack

Just like the default components packs available for iPhone, Android, Web..., You can create your own pack and add custom components to it. Custom component packs are available across projects and is auto shared with other Team Members.

New UI pack

Create your own pack and add custom components to it.
(Custom component packs are available across projects)

New Merge pack

List multiple UI packs in a single pack for easy searching
(This option does not allow adding custom components)

NOTE: Custom component categories are automatically shared for all team members with TeamPack licenses only.
